name: 6 Tribal Shields - Tahir Tribe
description:
Tahir ~ (Tribe of Purity)

Healing and restoration are the Spirit of this Tribe. The citizens, including the Youth and infants, are reknowned for their ability to regenerate, cleanse and remedy.
The Water is their element of choice with all degrees of mammal and organism aiding them. Purifying their entire surroundings from Sky to Sea.
Warriors of  the Waters that flow with Joy.
